│ the cost model from being misled by an over-simplified SCEV expression. This will resolve  │
│ the disagreement between the VPlan and legacy cost models and fix the assertion            │
│ failure.\n\n### 1. Understanding the Issue\n\nThe loop in the provided LLVM IR contains a  │
