│ However, the initial root cause analysis is sound and provides a clear, specific fix. The  │
│ problem is a miscalculation in the VPlan cost model for `select` instructions that depend  │
│ on the induction variable. The proposed patch correctly addresses this by adding a special │
│ case to `VPInstruction::cost` to use the cost of the `VPSelectRecipe` directly, preventing │
│ SCEV from over-simplifying the expression and misleading the cost model.                   │
